  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only <strong>ONE LIFE</strong> for condensed <strong>Fight </strong>through 11 intense missions with increasing difficulty, leading to the final battle as the Devastator's pilot. <strong>Upgrade</strong> your ship during battles by connecting components from defeated enemies. <strong>Collect</strong> all D-modules from destroyed flagships for the last attack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>11 weapon types:</strong> from splitting rockets to mines. Attach them to your ship during missions</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>42 enemy ships:</strong> from light cruisers to flagships </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>11</strong> <strong>missions near planets:</strong> difficulty grows with each mission</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Complete story:</strong> Enjoy jokes with your operator and AI during rare moments of safety</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333460/extras/8b08fb04d410fb3ae7a8e119e743bdce.avif?t=1744384432\" width=476 height=420 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for action and dodge bullets for your single life or <strong>try again</strong> from zero. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Salute <strong>o7</strong></p>",
